data.description: Spectacular home with private pool, located on the beautiful west coast and historic Orange River in Fort Myers. The neighborhood has a boating platform and its access connects with the great Caloosahatchee River. This property has a beautiful design with three large bedrooms and three elegantly renovated bathrooms and  kitchen. A large concrete patio to share under the shade with family and friends, barbecue area and a pool to relax. Huge garage with capacity for 2 cars and much more. A quiet west Florida neighborhood just minutes away for gulf sailing.
